%N A048917 Indices of hexagonal numbers which are also 9-gonal.
%C A048917 As n increases, the ratio of consecutive terms settles into an approximate 2-cycle with the ratio a(n)/a(n-1) bounded above and below by 2024 + 765*sqrt(7) and 8 + 3*sqrt(7) respectively. - _Ant King_, Dec 29 2011
